<L>__{exterior talley's car the intersection a few minutes later}
<A>__{talley is at his car with anders and two other officers, leigh metzger, a woman in her early thirties, and cliff campbell, a slender guy who looks like a retired security cop. talley is getting information reports both in person and over the radio }
<C>__{anders}
